verbose_text: Based on the microarray analysis, high levels of circRNA-003780, circRNA-010056 and circRNA-010231 in M1 cells and circRNA-003424, circRNA-013630, circRNA-001489 and circRNA-018127 in M2 cells with fold-change> 5 were selected and validated by RT-qPCR to confirm the results of the microarray analysis.
